1
00:00:03,809 --> 00:00:06,859
Shridhar Swami’s commentary

2
00:00:06,859 --> 00:00:09,109
differed from 
what was given previously,

3
00:00:09,109 --> 00:00:12,789
and people were wondering
whether or not it was authentic

4
00:00:13,069 --> 00:00:15,869
[Agent of the Infinite]

5
00:00:16,239 --> 00:00:18,159
and legitimate,
and should be accepted.

6
00:00:18,159 --> 00:00:22,529
And they submitted 
to the Bharadwaj deity of Mahadev Śiva.

7
00:00:22,529 --> 00:00:25,919
And they say, “This mantra came 
reverberating from the temple,

8
00:00:25,919 --> 00:00:28,779
where Śiva says, ‘I know 
the meaning of Bhagavatam,

9
00:00:28,779 --> 00:00:31,279
Śukadev knows the meaning 
of Bhagavatam,

10
00:00:31,279 --> 00:00:35,189
and Vyas, he may know 
and may not know.’”

11
00:00:35,189 --> 00:00:36,799
How is that possible?

12
00:00:36,799 --> 00:00:39,609
Vyas is the author!

13
00:00:39,807 --> 00:00:42,007
This is a very critical point.

14
00:00:42,007 --> 00:00:46,830
What’s coming down 
and passing through the agent 
may exceed the capacity of the agent,

15
00:00:46,830 --> 00:00:48,588
that’s also possible.

16
00:00:48,588 --> 00:00:51,398
This was Mahabrabhu’s response

17
00:00:51,398 --> 00:00:54,488
to Sanatana Goswami, 
when he was praising Mahaprabhu,

18
00:00:54,488 --> 00:00:55,951
“You’ve given ...

19
00:00:55,951 --> 00:00:59,831
Formerly, when You’ve met with Sarvabhauma,
he gave 9 explanation of atmarama,

20
00:00:59,831 --> 00:01:02,308
then You gave twice as many—18.

21
00:01:02,308 --> 00:01:03,411
That’s 27.

22
00:01:03,411 --> 00:01:09,111
But now You’ve given 60, not touching
any of 27 given previously.

23
00:01:09,690 --> 00:01:15,280
This is beyond human, it’s beyond
human capacity, it's Divine.”

24
00:01:16,110 --> 00:01:19,579
And Mahaprabhu is responding, 
“Oh Sanatana, don’t you know,

25
00:01:19,579 --> 00:01:22,679
one letter of Srimad-Bhagavatam
is infinite.

26
00:01:22,679 --> 00:01:25,809
A drop of the Infinite is infinite.

27
00:01:25,809 --> 00:01:30,929
So what is 60 explanations, 
why only?”

28
00:01:31,761 --> 00:01:37,141
Then He said, “And actually, by your
association and your necessity

29
00:01:38,251 --> 00:01:41,713
I feel another meaning 
awakening within Me.”

30
00:01:41,903 --> 00:01:45,093
And He gave the 61st explanation.

31
00:01:45,093 --> 00:01:48,348
That’s when He was saying, 
“By your necessity

32
00:01:48,348 --> 00:01:51,978
I feel another meaning 
awakening within Me.

33
00:01:51,978 --> 00:01:56,048
And what’s passing through Me 
I may not understand at all.

34
00:01:56,048 --> 00:02:00,812
But what I can understand is that 
Krishna wants to grace you through Me,

35
00:02:00,812 --> 00:02:03,111
that much I’m certain of.

36
00:02:03,111 --> 00:02:06,146
But what’s passing 
through Me may be beyond ...

37
00:02:06,146 --> 00:02:10,220
maybe I understand, 
maybe I don’t understand.”

38
00:02:11,930 --> 00:02:18,640
That is the nature 
of Divine revelation.

39
00:02:19,709 --> 00:02:23,370
So the devotees are offering
themselves as agents.

40
00:02:23,370 --> 00:02:24,760
Just as in the Bhagavad-gita,

41
00:02:24,760 --> 00:02:28,047
nimitta-mātraḿ bhava savya-sācin 
[Bg: 11.33]

42
00:02:28,047 --> 00:02:32,857
And Arjuna offers himself 
as Kṛṣṇa’s agent.

